{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_630.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "(Oh, I know! I should ask Linca about what she thought about slaying the dragon.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Linca, about that time we slew the dragon..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Did it feel like you reached your goal, or did you at least feel some kind of satisfaction?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I thought that I would come to some kind of understanding after defeating the dragon, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "In the end, I understood nothing.<CR>It seems like that was not what<CR>I wanted to do after all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But it became clear...that that was not the right solution."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I probably do not actually like fighting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh...that's a little unexpected.<CR>Hmm, but I guess it's not surprising."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I thought that I only had my sword,<CR>but maybe that was because my sword<CR>is all I know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "There's nothing \"maybe\" about it. That's what I've always been telling you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "So it is, I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Well, you get a \"well done\" just for realizing that. Take your time and search for what you want to do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "What I want to do... To protect Marion is what I want to do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But you're talking about your duty.<CR>I'm talking about something else."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "No, even if it was not my duty, I want to always stay by your side forever."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Th-That's not realistic. To even stay together for 10 or 20 years is‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I am fine with either 10 or 20 years,<CR>if I am with Marion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Goodness... Don't say such things with a straight face..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x127,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, we drifted away from the topic about how you were going to find your goal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "No. If my goal is to be with Marion, then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It means I have already achieved it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "A-Absolutely not!<CR>That's kind of cheating..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Marion, do you not like being with me...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x99,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Oh, jeez. That's not it. This is this, and that is that, so you have to find your goal!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Marion got angry...<CR>And I got scolded again today..."
        }
    ]
}